	rep\\\, and immersive camps designed to build “forever skills” like logic 
	and collaborative problem-solving. \\nWe will have special opening day wor
	kshops\\\, exclusive discounts and offers\\\, and light snacks.\n\nhttps:/
	/discovermagnolia.org/event/grand-opening-ai-robotics-academy/\n\nFrom Dis
	cover Magnolia
